SEARCH
Package scoring

Class FlightData

java.lang.Object
scoring.FlightData
public class FlightData extends Object
Contains important flight data for success scoring. Used to manage and keep data in memory until it is no longer needed. Please note, this class purposefully has no knowledge of the units of measurement for the data it holds.
